               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origDate notBefore="1750" notAfter="1848"/>
                     A small-size Four Gospels (smaller than <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFabb95">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien d'Abbadie 95</ref>). The name
