                    <provenance>The manuscript was possibly in possession of <persName cert="medium" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13441WaldaYohannes">Walda Yoḥannǝs</persName> before it was
                      acquired by <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1071dAbbadi">Antoine d'Abbadie</persName>
                      sometime between <date>1840</date> and <date>1848</date>.
                    </provenance>
                  <acquisition>The manuscript entered the Bibliothèque nationale in
                    <date>1902</date>.
